TextEng: "Durnan called for heroes. I'm here to do the right thing."
Text: "더난이 영웅을 불렀어. 올바른 일을 하러 왔지."

TextEng: "Do you know anything about what's going on in Waterdeep?"
Text: "워터딥에서 무슨 일이 벌어지는지 아는 게 있어?"

TextEng: "Tell me about these friends of yours."
"Just keep your temper in check or I put you in your place."
Text: "성질 좀 누르고 있어, 안 그러면 내가 혼쭐을 내줄 테니까."

TextEng: "If there's a chance to kill something, I'll always take it."
"If it ever becomes your business, I'll let you know."
"To be honest, I don't really know why I'm here."
Text: "솔직히 말하면, 내가 왜 여기 있는지 잘 모르겠어."

TextEng: "I care what happens to Waterdeep, even if you don't."
Text: "난 워터딥에 무슨 일이 일어나는지 신경 쓰여, 네가 안 그러더라도."

TextEng: "I'm always looking for adventure, if the reward is right."
